Nemesis
games.info: Nemesis is a 1-5 player board game which may be played fully co-op or semi-co-op.

expansions.name: Aftermath
expansions.info: Aftermath is an expansion which takes place after the end of a game of Nemesis, hence the name. A new crew boards Nemesis to investigate what previously occured. Unbeknownst to them, a threat still remains.

expansions.name: Void Seeders
expansions.info: Void Seeders is an expansion which replaces the Intruders with a new enemy type, Void Seeders. The crew is tasked with taking on a challening enemy that inflitrates their minds, causing illusions. May be used with Nemesis or Aftermath.

expansions.name: Kings
expansions.info: Kings is a cosmetic expansion which replaces the Queens of each race with a male counterpart.
